    "Details": "The Boreas R variant, also known as the Amirault, is a tribute to the renowned Hells Horses MechWarrior, Joshua Amirault. This variant features an Endo Steel frame that enhances its durability without sacrificing mobility. Its original weapon systems have been replaced with four LRM 15 missile launchers and three ER Medium Lasers, providing devastating long-range firepower coupled with moderate close-range capability. The Boreas R also boasts an advanced cooling system that utilizes prototype heat sinks, which allow the MechWarrior to fire its weapons without worrying about heat management issues.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: QuadVee Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>",
